The paper discusses the role of teaching in artificial intelligence and proposes a framework for optimizing teaching strategies using reinforcement learning. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
